CONTACT_FORM_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Let us know how we can help facilitate your paper cup trading needs.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What is a paper cup trading marketplace?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: It's an online platform that allows buyers and sellers to trade used or collectible paper cups. People can buy, sell or trade unique or rare paper cup designs.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: How does the trading process work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Sellers list their paper cups with descriptions and pictures. Buyers can browse listings and make offers or purchase cups at the listed price. Safe payment and shipping is facilitated through the marketplace.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: What types of paper cups are traded?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: All kinds of paper cups are traded - from common disposable cups to rare promotional cups from events or limited edition designer cups. Collectible, vintage, and unique cups are highly sought after.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is there a fee to use the marketplace?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, the marketplace charges a small commission fee on completed sales to cover operational costs. The fees are clearly stated and are a standard practice for online trading platforms.

FAQ_TITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Welcome to the Paper Cup Trading Marketplace
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Your one-stop shop for buying, selling, and trading paper cups
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What types of paper cups can I trade?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our marketplace supports trading of all kinds of paper cups - from plain white to printed designs, hot cups to cold cups, and everything in between.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How do I list a paper cup for sale?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Just create an account, snap some photos of your cup, provide a description and asking price, and list it on our easy-to-use selling platform.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: What payment methods do you accept?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: We accept all major credit cards as well as PayPal for maximum convenience when buying paper cups.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Do you offer shipping for purchased cups?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, we partner with major shipping carriers to safely deliver your new paper cup purchases right to your doorstep.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How can I get the best deals on cups?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Be sure to check our daily deals section and sign up for our email newsletter to receive alerts on new listings and special discounts.
